{"tid":194584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人惡習問題","createTime":"2017-04-10T05:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T06:58:50.000Z","uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22bf2fb7de0091b7746268f83444d00203067baf","tid":194584,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"唔明點解到呢個年代，大家都仲係唔習慣去快餐店食野唔會順手執埋d野<br />\n成枱都係食淨既野，職員睇唔到就要下一手執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6aa6ce8b182e3e4d782e5dfbd602fd37cf0f55","tid":194584,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:25:28.000Z","msg":"同意 <br />\n仲有大聲講野又鍾意橫衝直撞"},{"pid":"210a4573e464fff799442cd6abdc7d4cd92e5fdf","tid":194584,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"留名睇世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c55cc8ed6a163dcb0e8b9ddb647cb72eff269a2","tid":194584,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意 <br />\n仲有大聲講野又鍾意橫衝直撞</blockquote><br />\n坐早班巴士d大叔大大聲順計<br />\n坐鐵路d人未出晒就狗衝"},{"pid":"65c2f56125f38a2cfc0bf6bbb2d6cc8bc2df6a35","tid":194584,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:34:22.000Z","msg":"點睇我成日食到淨番杯可樂 STAFF主動問我洗唔洗收左佢?"},{"pid":"1976cd002c69a06d7ce3f4c2307f813218f12bbc","tid":194584,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇我成日食到淨番杯可樂 STAFF主動問我洗唔洗收左佢?</blockquote><br />\nstaff一向有問題，好多時都係睇心情做野<br />\n但食客自己食完野都應該有小小手尾，唔好留到一枱都係野比下個人"},{"pid":"44a1a9fad04fc0bec7e92d856fc6fd915c120ca6","tid":194584,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:57:39.000Z","msg":"係芬蘭遇到好多香港人<br />\n永遠係最大聲最嘈嘈閉個班<br />\n啲廢中大媽係候機室唔撚帶耳機就播蝗劇睇, 嘈撚住哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671504b6af084926f86f7e0f7960b0d64f10e886","tid":194584,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:58:50.000Z","msg":"同中國人差唔多"}]}